---
title: Beef Tostadas Supremo with Green Pepper, Lime Crema & Pico de Gallo
description: Can’t decide between the flavors of your favorite taco and the satisfying crunch-factor of a plate of nachos? Enter the tostada! In this recipe, you’ll layer tortillas with two types of cheese and toast in the oven until melty for a flat, golden, crispy base. Then, you’ll layer on toppings—spiced pork and sautéed veggies, pico de gallo, and tangy lime crema.
